Tom McTevia, 42, and his passenger and best friend, Tina Hoisington, 45, died after their ATV plunged from an Idaho overlook on Sunday . 
 Witnesses said they got too close to the edge while posing for a photo . 
 McTevia was left paralyzed in another ATV accident 11 years earlier . 
 But the former cop and Navy veteran continued to stay active and advocated for better trails for people in wheelchairs . 
 